    .page-house._developers
      .page-house__content
        .h1 About the company "Terem"
        .text-truncate(data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="50")
          .text-truncate__wrapper.text-hidden 
            p
              |Since 2010, the construction company "Terem" has been designing and constructing buildings from laminated veneer lumber,
              |aerated concrete blocks and using frame technology. She has built over 50,000 cottages, summer houses, bathhouses, and small
              |сbuildings in the Moscow region and other regions.
            p
              |The company's catalog contains 720 projects. Each one can be modified: add a terrace or veranda,
              |a room or an entire floor, move the walls a little or change the layout.
            p
              |Today, Terem provides a full range of services: construction of wooden houses, individual design,
              |Completion and reconstruction, installation of utilities, lending and insurance, land selection, and much more.
            p
              |Today, Terem provides a full range of services: construction of wooden houses, individual design,
